just_use registry.go

# label: CANONICAL
# role: encodes domain knowledge

Single source of truth for hand-registered CRUD pages (PageDef + GetPages).
Nav bar, index, and tour all read from this list. GetPages is a function,
not a var, to avoid an init cycle: Pages → handlers → PageHeader → Pages.

Generated pages appended via `generatedPages` (see registry_generated.go)
so this hardcoded list shrinks as crudgen coverage grows. RegisterPages
wires all routes plus the non-page infra (tour, quicknav, sse/*, /).
